"n.赔偿；保证 【考】 mollification : soothe / indemnity : secure(减轻为了缓和/赔偿 为了获得) n. 保修; 保证(不受毁坏、丢失或伤害); (对毁坏或伤害的)赔偿 【记】in不, demn = damn该死的, ity－不该死的, 因为有保修 【参】indemnify(v 赔偿) = reimburse; condemn(vt 判刑; 谴责)indemnification(n 保护; 补偿物) = recompense = reparation 【类】mollification: soothe = indemnity: secure缓和n 对缓和v = 保证n 对保证v 【记】in + damage 将损失抵消；in反意 + condemn谴责,或 damn(英语骂人)→不遗责，不骂人，还要补偿 indemnity (n.)  mid-15c., from Middle French indemnité (14c.), from Late Latin indemnitatem (nominative indemnitas) ""security for damage,"" from Latin indemnis ""unhurt, undamaged,"" from in- ""not, opposite of, without"" (see in- (1)) + damnum ""damage"" (see damn)."
